 ://www.theverge.com/24198268/amazon-prime-day-best-cheap-tech-deals-under-50-2024&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;Y34rxR&quot;>;这是 SoundLink Flex 迄今为止的最低价格，它是&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23022617/best-bluetooth-speakers&quot;>;我们首选的蓝牙扬声器&lt;/a>; 低于 200 美元。 Bose 的彩色扬声器占地面积很小，可以轻松放入包中并随身携带，但听起来却像是一个更大的扬声器。它的声音优美、低音丰富，不会让人觉得“那是……”&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17/24200551/ amazon-prime-day-bose-soundlink-flex-bluetooth-speaker-soundbar-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17/24200551/amazon-prime-day-bose-soundlink-flex-bluetooth-speaker-soundbar-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17/24200551/amazon-prime-day-bose-soundlink-flex-bluetooth-speaker-soundbar-deal-sale</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-17T16:41:34-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-17T16:41:34-04:00</updated><title>亚马逊 Prime Day 最佳 Apple Watch 优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;女性手臂上的 Apple Watch SE (2022) 和 Apple Watch Ultra&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/hSbeh70TDkE826CIPdrN3565imw=/0x0:2040x1360/ 1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73463622/226292_Apple_Watch_SE_PHO_akrales_0306.5.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片由 Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot; 66SMfr&quot;>;Apple Watch 全年都会出现限时折扣，但是 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24191617/amazon-prime-day-tech-deals-guide- 2024&quot;>;亚马逊 Prime Day&lt;/a>; 为人们提供了一次购买大多数可用型号的优惠的机会。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id =&quot;lrQEpx&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 2024 年亚马逊 Prime Day 指南&quot;,&quot;url&quot; :&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24191617/amazon-prime-